{"tid":604789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【選妃片】直擊峇里島金錢豹　3百佳麗坐玻璃櫥窗勾客","createTime":"2018-03-25T05:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T08:20:33.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7c48957ee0412b076af8720831985fd0e7dcfc","tid":604789,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"峇里島地區一共有6家KTV，他的占地有3甲2，目前排行最大也最豪華。第2大占地1千坪，其他4家皆約數百坪。草創初期包廂僅10間，陸續拓建至今，才有44間大小廂。這裡與台灣酒店一樣大，但風格不相同，最大的特色就是高達300人的佳麗。<br />\n他表示，佳麗年齡平均在18至26歲，大部分來自是爪哇島或蘇門答臘島，因為生活困苦，認為外籍遊客比較有錢，給的小費比較優豁，所以都跑過來這裡上班。想要多賺小費除了靠打扮外，就要靠自己的手腕。<br />\n康榮旋指出，他的客人中有三成外籍遊客、三成是來自外地的印尼人、四成是峇里島當地人。客人點1名小姐，價碼從美金30元至60元（約900至1800元）都有，依人氣指數而定。小姐當天若是全場坐冷板凳，他會付美金20元作為補償。而峇里島的白領上班族每月平均薪水為240元美金（約台幣7200元）。也就是說，小姐就算天天坐冷板凳，也只要12天就能賺到白領上班族的平均月薪。<br />\n客人平常選妃時嚴禁拍照錄影，《蘋果》當晚9點徵得同意，入內拍攝時已過了選妃巔峰期，櫥窗裡的佳麗只剩20名沒被帶出場，每位佳麗臉上全透露出一絲哀怨，翹著美腿，偶爾抓抓頭髮、玩玩指甲，相互喬奶聊天。拍攝約10分鐘下來，前後只有5名男子站在櫥窗外，看了1分鐘後就離開，沒有埋單。<br />\n康榮旋說：「環肥燕瘦各有人愛」如果小姐整晚都坐「冷板凳」我們也愛莫能助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180325/1319432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180325%2F1319432&d=rnLJWTJRiABdN9x9mvKqb%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=b07d01f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180325%2F1319432&h=909082f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180325/1319432</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180325/640_6bdc53940456732d5592c8462f86dd1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180325%2F640_6bdc53940456732d5592c8462f86dd1b.jpg&h=8f5f9015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180325/640_101bb26e9bc8b270518760e8ef393005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180325%2F640_101bb26e9bc8b270518760e8ef393005.jpg&h=104b9e5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180325/640_0a5b528b08bcbafd8fa8a435d86bf40f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180325%2F640_0a5b528b08bcbafd8fa8a435d86bf40f.jpg&h=19bb6ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180325/640_6f2b62a2a80f25d02675c95f03f7f899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180325%2F640_6f2b62a2a80f25d02675c95f03f7f899.jpg&h=5cb1486d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180325/640_3b77e9eb6f48151a2739fe4a1bc120d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180325%2F640_3b77e9eb6f48151a2739fe4a1bc120d5.jpg&h=33cf3fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 質素"},{"pid":"c1c0743a8fcdfb1365b7c6149056307913aea8b5","tid":604789,"uid":44454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:31:37.000Z","msg":"最尾嗰張會部都係男人"},{"pid":"c67f7b9b9793ee957750e58002e150e6fc784b73","tid":604789,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b96b5e196532f58c6c83eb6779ffd77ece0dc3e","tid":604789,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/134132_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F134132_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bafbb146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecb33d88dfdf22218e7db422c1f95293e0ac3993","tid":604789,"uid":53601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:42:51.000Z"